items.text: The **snooker season 1994/1995** was a series of [[LINK|lang_en|Snooker|snooker]] tournaments played during the years 1994 and 1995. The following table outlines the results for ranking events and the invitational events.

The top 16 of the world rankings, these players automatically played in the final rounds of the world ranking events and were invited for the Masters.[[CITE|45|https://web.archive.org/web/20120313150539/http://www.cajt.pwp.blueyonder.co.uk/HistoricRank2.html]][[CITE|46|http://www.snooker.org/rnk/rk_9495.shtml]][[CITE|47|/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number]]
